description: This learning path is tailor-made for Crypto Startups with focus on Bitcoin and Ethereum. We will go into the basics of bitcoin and ethereum and also immerse ourselves in programming, decentralized finance and more. You will gain a solid basic knowledge in programming, which will be important for you as the founder of a startup, regardless of whether you yourself are a coder or employ skills for it
title: Crypto Startups BTC/ETH
